Usage:
     pwc2igv.pl --input fisher.results --output fisher.results.igv --log-transform

Options:
    --input
        The input file. Has to be the output of either "fst-sliding.pl" or
        "fisher-test.pl". Mandatory parameter

    --output
        The output file. Must have the extension ".igv". Can be directly
        loaded into the IGV. Mandatory parameter

    --window-size
        specify the size of the window; optional parameter; default=1

    --log-transform
        flag; log transform the measure (-log10). This may be especially
        useful for the results of <fisher-test.pl>; optional parameter;
        default=off

    --test
        Run the unit tests for this script.

    --help
        Display help for this script

